    "body" : "<p>Use this code:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static void main(String[] args) {\n    String test = \"A|B|C||D\";\n\n    String[] result = test.split(\"\\\\|\");\n\n    for (String s : result) {\n        System.out.println(\"&gt;\" + s + \"&lt;\");\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
